# Trading Brain Architecture

## Module Map (~60 files in `app/services/trading/`)

### Core Orchestration
- `learning.py` — Pattern mining, learning cycle orchestration, brain stats (~8k lines)
- `learning_cycle_architecture.py` — Canonical step/cluster definitions for graph + status
- `learning_cycle_report.py` — LLM/fallback cycle report generation
- `brain_resource_budget.py` — Per-cycle caps for fetches/miners/injects

### Brain Worker (`scripts/brain_worker.py`)
- Main loop: acquire file lock → `run_learning_cycle(status)` → `run_subtasks` → sleep
- Subtask modes: `alpha_decay` (every 3 cycles), `signal_refresh` (every 1), `fast_backtest` (every 1), `retention` (every 12)
- Status JSON: `data/brain_worker_status.json`
- Control signals: `brain_worker_stop`, `_pause`, `_wake` (file + DB)
- Idle sleep: 60s if active queue, else `--interval` minutes; chunked with heartbeat/stop checks

